### Get all media for a product
GET http://localhost:8000/api/media/product/1

### Get single media by ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/media/1

### Create media (admin)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/media
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "mediaUrl": "https://example.com/images/product1.jpg",
  "mediaType": "image"
}

### Update media (admin)
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/media/1/product/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mediaUrl": "https://example.com/images/product1-updated.jpg"
}

### Delete media (admin)
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/media/1/product/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN